Amy Jackson is a British actress and model. Jackson began her career as a model, winning the Miss Teen World competition in 2009 and the Miss Liverpool title in 2010. She then ventured into acting, primarily appearing in Indian films. Amy Jackson made her acting debut in the Tamil film "Madrasapattinam" in 2010. She gained recognition for her roles in Tamil films such as "Ekk Deewana Tha," "I," and "Theri." She has also worked in other regional language films like Telugu and Hindi.
